"""Per-country China-relations events (generated by per-country subagents from historian knowledge),
verified against the Tsinghua relations series: an event is 'verified' if the Tsinghua score moves
notably (|delta| >= 1.0 on the -9..+9 scale) within ~12 months around it. All events kept; the flag
is informational. Writes events.csv for the Historical Trends page."""
import json, pandas as pd

